data.value: EasyNodeJS is a free to use, easy to understand Node.JS Project Editor. You select your project folder, and all the files for your project will appear. Selecting a file from the list will show everything in that file. You can save your code, and it will write directly to that file, when it writes to the file, you will be able to edit all your other files! This project is a part of EasyHTML, and is inspired by the Vapid project.
